Kpɔɖeŋu kawoe ɖee fia be amegbetɔ madeblibowo ate ŋu awɔ woƒe tiatiawɔblɔɖea ŋu dɔ le mɔ si dea bubu Mawu ŋu nu?
Kissitɔwo ƒe peni wonyea?
